<TD width=441 valign=top bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><TABLE width=441 valign=top cellpadding=0 cellspacing=10 border=0><TR><TD><FONT FACE="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" color="#000000">

<h2><font face="arial,helvetica">Royal Real Estate</font></h2>

<h3><font face="arial,helvetica">Beijing's imperial palace complex gives a new meaning to 'inner city'</font></h3>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="5">
	<tr valign="top">
		<td><a href="/SPECIALS/1999/china.50/dispatches/images/link.bruce.kennedy.jpg"><img src="/SPECIALS/1999/china.50/dispatches/images/bruce.kennedy.jpg" alt="Kennedy" width="87" height="87" border="0"></a></td>
		<td><font face="arial,helvetica" size="2" color="#000000"><b>
By <a href="#bio"><font color="#0033CC">Bruce Kennedy</font></a><br>
CNN Interactive
		</b></font></td>
	</tr>
</table>


<TABLE ALIGN=right CELLPADDING=5 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0><TR><TD>
<TABLE WIDTH=214 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0> <TR><TD colspan=2>
<!--===========IMAGE============-->
<IMG SRC="top.ancestor.hall.jpg" ALT="Hall of Worshipping Ancestors" WIDTH="214" HEIGHT="164" BORDER="0" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0">
<!--===========/IMAGE===========-->
</TD></TR><TR><TD><FONT FACE="verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif" SIZE="-2" color="#000000"><B>
<!--===========CAPTION==========-->
The Hall of Worshipping Ancestors (Feng Xian Dian): Used by emperors for memorial rites, the hall now houses an exhibition of imperial relics
<!--===========/CAPTION=========-->
</B></FONT></TD><TD width=12>&nbsp;</TD></TR></TABLE>
</TD></TR></TABLE>

<P>
BEIJING (CNN)-- It was the day after China's National Day, and everyone who lives in the capital city apparently was out for a walk. The area around Tiananmen Square was packed. Many people carried China's national flag, heading to the square to examine the floats from the huge parade a day earlier.
</P>

<P>
For my part, I wanted to see the <A HREF="javascript:openWindow('link.map.html','windowname','toolbar=no,location=no,directories=no,status=no,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes,resizable=no,width=510,height=400')"><font color="#0033CC">Forbidden City</FONT></A>. The last time I had visited was 10 years ago, following the crackdown in Tiananmen, when a handful of journalists were the only patrons of the palace grounds.
</P>

<!-- also -->
